      <div class="SOTTO_PARA"><a name="DUCa5ab97e02b7410058c2987d9909970d2"></a>Removing the rear shock absorber
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e7683"> </a>Remove the rear left side body panel (<a href="77993.html#DUCa04e3f602a971005810ecc3160c450d2">Removing the side body panels and tail guard</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e7688"> </a>Remove the rear mudguard (<a href="78010.html#DUC24c226b82aab10058bbef20939ae18d2">Removing the rear mudguard</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e7693"> </a>Remove the silencer (<a href="79882.html#DUC408fed082b2310058d65a5fdf30dcfc4">Removing the silencer</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e7698"> </a>Remove the rear wheel (<a href="78610.html#DUC64d8fb602aeb100584ccb8bb6ec21ad2">Removing the rear wheel</a>).
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e7704"> </a>Loosen screws (2) to remove preload adjustment knob (A).
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
