         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e7709"> </a>Remove the tie (C) and release the cable.
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e7711"> </a>To remove the rear shock absorber from the motorcycle, loosen the top screw (3) and the bottom screw (4).
         </div>
      </div>
